---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Complete Guide to Executive Coach Marketing Automation in Canada | Lead Flow North" description="Fill your coaching practice, nurture high-value prospects, and build a referral engine without sacrificing the personal touch.">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/professional-services/executive-coaches" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Executive Coaches
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-rose-100 text-rose-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Executive Coaches</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">10 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          The Complete Guide to Executive Coach Marketing Automation
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          Fill your coaching practice, nurture high-value prospects, and build a referral engine without sacrificing the personal touch.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          
          <p class="lead text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Executive coaching is deeply personal. But the business development behind it doesn't have to be. Automation handles the mechanics so you can focus on transformation.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Building Trust Before the Call</h2>

          <p>
            High-level executives need to know, like, and trust you before investing in coaching. Automated nurture sequences—philosophy shares, success stories, thought leadership—warm prospects before the discovery conversation.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Enhancing the Client Journey</h2>

          <p>
            Coaching happens in sessions, but growth happens between them. Automated touchpoints—session prep, accountability nudges, progress celebrations—enhance the transformation without adding to your calendar.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">Referrals Are Your Lifeblood</h2>

          <p>
            Your best clients come from existing client referrals. Systematic asks at milestone moments—breakthrough sessions, engagement completions—generate consistent introductions to qualified executives.
          </p>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-600 to-pink-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Fill Your Practice?</h3>
            <p class="text-rose-100 mb-6">
              Get a free consultation and see exactly how we'd automate prospect nurturing while keeping your authentic voice.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 text-rose-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
